{
    "title": "Popup Links",
    "label": "Popup Links",
    "description": "X3 uses the popup for galleries, but you can also use it to display images and media in your page content. The X3 popup is perfect for images, but can also be used for videos and html content.",
    "image": "ocean-1.jpg",
    "content": "**Image**\nSimply add the data-popup attribute in your link.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\"><code><a href=\"ocean-1.jpg\" data-popup>image<\/a><\/code><\/pre>\n<a href=\"{{path}}ocean-1.jpg\" class=\"button small\" data-popup data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\">image<\/a>\n\n**Title**\nInclude the data-popup-title attribute in your link.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\"><code><a href=\"ocean-1.jpg\" data-popup-title=\"Big ocean!\">title<\/a><\/code><\/pre>\n<a href=\"{{path}}ocean-1.jpg\" class=\"button small\" data-popup-title=\"Big ocean!\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\">title<\/a>\n\n**Groups**\nGroup your links into a single popup by adding them inside a data-popup-container.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\"><code>\n<div data-popup-container><br>\n<a href=\"ocean-1.jpg\">ocean 1<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"ocean-2.jpg\">ocean 2<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"ocean-3.jpg\">ocean 3<\/a><br>\n<\/div>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<div data-popup-container>\n<a href=\"{{path}}ocean-1.jpg\" class=\"button small\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\">ocean 1<\/a> <a href=\"{{path}}ocean-2.jpg\" class=\"button small\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1360\">ocean 2<\/a> <a href=\"{{path}}ocean-3.jpg\" class=\"button small\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\">ocean 3<\/a>\n<\/div>\n\nOr use the \"rel\" attribute to group items.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\"><code>\n<a href=\"ocean-1.jpg\" data-popup rel=\"mypopup\">ocean 1<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"ocean-2.jpg\" data-popup rel=\"mypopup\">ocean 2<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"ocean-3.jpg\" data-popup rel=\"mypopup\">ocean 3<\/a><br>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<a href=\"{{path}}ocean-1.jpg\" data-popup class=\"button small\" rel=\"mypopup\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\">ocean 1<\/a> <a href=\"{{path}}ocean-2.jpg\" data-popup class=\"button small\" rel=\"mypopup\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1360\">ocean 2<\/a> <a href=\"{{path}}ocean-3.jpg\" data-popup class=\"button small\" rel=\"mypopup\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\">ocean 3<\/a>\n\n**Image Links**\nYou can use images in your links, which provides a nice zoom effect.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\">\n<code>\n<a href=\"ocean-1.jpg\" data-popup><img src=\"ocean-1.jpg\"><\/a>\n<\/code>\n<\/pre>\n<a href=\"{{path}}ocean-1.jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\" data-popup><img src=\"{{path}}ocean-1.jpg\" class=\"x3-style-frame\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n\nYou can also group your image links.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\"><code>\n<div data-popup-container><br>\n<a href=\"ocean-1.jpg\" data-popup><img src=\"ocean-1.jpg\"><\/a><br>\n<a href=\"ocean-2.jpg\" data-popup><img src=\"ocean-2.jpg\"><\/a><br>\n<a href=\"ocean-2.jpg\" data-popup><img src=\"ocean-2.jpg\"><\/a><br>\n<\/div>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<div class=\"row\" data-popup-container style=\"margin-bottom: 3rem\">\n  <div class=\"small-4 columns\"><a href=\"{{path}}ocean-1.jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\"><img src=\"{{path}}ocean-1.jpg\" class=\"x3-style-frame\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/div>\n  <div class=\"small-4 columns\"><a href=\"{{path}}ocean-2.jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1360\"><img src=\"{{path}}ocean-2.jpg\" class=\"x3-style-frame\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/div>\n\t<div class=\"small-4 columns\"><a href=\"{{path}}ocean-3.jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\"><img src=\"{{path}}ocean-3.jpg\" class=\"x3-style-frame\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n**Youtube**\nThe popup is useful for displaying videos from Youtube or Vimeo.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\"><code>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/G46ygBKsTZI\" data-popup>Youtube<\/a>\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/G46ygBKsTZI\" data-popup class=\"button small\">Youtube<\/a>\n\n**Video mp4**\nYou can also display local-hosted mp4 video files.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\">\n<code>\n<a href=\"video.mp4\" data-popup>video<\/a>\n<\/code>\n<\/pre>\n<a href=\"\/content\/examples\/features\/sample\/SampleVideo_720x480_1mb.mp4\" data-popup class=\"button small\">video<\/a>\n\n**Html content**\nYou can also use the popup to display basic html content.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\">\n<code>\n<a href=\"#\" data-popup-content=\"<h2>Custom Content<\/h2><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla in lorem vel turpis tincidunt varius. Aenean molestie sem velit, quis accumsan sapien molestie non. In nec quam tortor.<\/p>\">html<\/a>\n<\/code>\n<\/pre>\n<a href=\"#\" data-popup-content=\"<h2>Custom Content<\/h2><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla in lorem vel turpis tincidunt varius. Aenean molestie sem velit, quis accumsan sapien molestie non. In nec quam tortor.<\/p>\" class=\"button small\">html<\/a>\n\n**Website**\nYou can also open external websites in the popup, if allowed to load inside an iframe.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\">\n<code>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.bbc.com\/\" data-popup>bbc.com<\/a>\n<\/code>\n<\/pre>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.bbc.com\/\" data-popup class=\"button small\">website<\/a>\n\n**Advanced options**\nThe content popup comes with plenty advanced options.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\">\n<code>\n<a href=\"#\" data-popup-content=\"Hello world!\">html content in popup<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-image=\"true\">force image type<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-history=\"false\">disable url#hash history<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-pid=\"URL-ID\">assign custom url#hash id<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-main-class=\"css-class\">assign custom popup CSS class<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-class=\"css-class\">assign custom CSS class for html<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-download=\"true\">enable download button<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-fullscreen=\"false\">disable fullscreen button<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-play=\"false\">disable slideshow play button<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-zoom=\"false\">disable zoom button<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-arrow=\"false\">disable arrow control buttons<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-original=\"original_SRC\">assign option source for zoom<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-loop=\"false\">disable popup loop<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-transition=\"pop\">assign popup transition<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-play-transition=\"fade\">assign slideshow transition<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-caption-hide=\"false\">disable caption autohide<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-bg-color=\"#000099\">assign custom background color<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-bg=\"#990000\">custom background for specific image<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-bg-image=\"true\">assign background color from images<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-caption-style=\"box\">assign caption style<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-caption-align=\"center-left\">assign caption position<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-popup-caption=\"false\">disable caption<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-width=\"2048\">inform source img width for zoom effect<\/a><br>\n<a href=\"SRC\" data-height=\"1365\">inform source img height for zoom effect<\/a><br>\n<\/code>\n<\/pre>\n\n---\n\n## Browser Popup Window\nYou can also open links in brower popup windows. Although not as elegant as the X3 popup, it is more functional and has no restrictions when opening external websites.\n<pre data-lang=\"html\">\n<code>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.flamepix.com\/\" data-popup-window>Flamepix.com<\/a>\n<\/code>\n<\/pre>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.flamepix.com\/\" data-popup-window class=\"button small\">Flamepix.com<\/a>\n\nYou can also change the popup window size (does not work on mobile):\n<pre data-lang=\"html\">\n<code>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.flamepix.com\/\" data-popup-window=\"name,1100,800\">Flamepix.com<\/a>\n<\/code>\n<\/pre>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/www.flamepix.com\/\" data-popup-window=\"name,1100,800\" class=\"button small\">Flamepix.com large popup<\/a>\n\n\n---\n\n## X3 gallery popups\nThe X3 gallery uses a slightly more advanced version of the popup.\n",
